  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 465.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- but still, it was a little bit more-- a little better organized.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least we were able to know exactly the different rules that they start instituting, one after the other one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Befehl, that is in German, they were right after one befehl after the other one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was like I mentioned to you, turn over all the valuables, that Jews cannot walk on the sidewalk, they have to walk-- the Jews can only walk during certain hours of the day they can go out, that Jews [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] cannot come into-- to stores.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They have only a certain hour to come into the stores, that they're limited to a certain amount of money, they're limited to-- to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They-- they took basically away all all the rights.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Jews suddenly became like nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, like dust.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we had-- we had-- they re-instituted the Lithuanian currency, because, as you know, when the Russians came, they had this currency changed to rubles and chervontsy.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now they have re-instituted the Lithuanian, but they also brought in the German-- later on, the German-- German marks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- and in order to survive, what we had to do is we had to take some of our belongings and to exchange that for bread or for anything.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And and those people who had certain valuables-- beyond the fact that they have-- they have turned in, but certain people have risked their lives and they still kept certain valuables, which later on helped them to-- to survive in a certain way.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Afterwards, I mean, they-- the next step was that many-- in this-- in this interim time, there were thousands were killed and murdered, actually.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
